OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772474763
OL,3,CMan to admit killing Chloe Mitchell,
OL,4,Ccourt told
OL,6,FA man is to plead guilty to killing
OL,7,FChloe Mitchell by reason of diminished
OL,8,Fresponsibility, a court has been told.
OL,10,FBrandon John Rainey, formerly of James
OL,11,FStreet, Ballymena, was due to go on
OL,12,Ftrial at Belfast Crown Court on March
OL,13,F9, 2026, for the murder of Ms
OL,14,FMitchell, which he denies.
OL,16,FThe 29-year-old further denies a
OL,17,Fcharge of attempting to prevent "the
OL,18,Flawful and decent burial of a deceased
OL,19,Fbody'' on the same date on June 3,
OL,20,F2023.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
