PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772474763
OL,3,CMan to admit killing Chloe Mitchell,
OL,4,Ccourt told
OL,6,FHowever, during an emergency hearing
OL,7,Fat Belfast Crown Court before Madam
OL,8,FJustice McBride on Friday, senior
OL,9,Fdefence counsel Neil Connor KC said he
OL,10,Fwanted to update the court following a
OL,11,Freview of proceedings on Thursday.
OL,13,F"The reason for the unexpected hearing
OL,14,Fthis morning is that myself, my junior
OL,15,Fcounsel Mr Neil Moore and my
OL,16,Finstructing solicitor Mr James
OL,17,FBallentine, had a scheduled
OL,18,Fconsultation with Mr Rainey yesterday
OL,19,Fafternoon,'' said Mr Connor.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772474763
OL,3,CMan to admit killing Chloe Mitchell,
OL,4,Ccourt told
OL,6,F"That consultation took a perhaps
OL,7,Funexpected turn to the extent that my
OL,8,Finstructions from Mr Rainey have
OL,9,Fchanged which is likely to have a
OL,10,Fsubstantial impact on the trial.''
OL,12,FMr Connor told Madam Justice McBride
OL,13,Fthat he had an application to amend
OL,14,Fthe previously lodged defence
OL,15,Fstatement.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772474763
OL,3,CMan to admit killing Chloe Mitchell,
OL,4,Ccourt told
OL,6,F"That document reflects the change in
OL,7,Finstructions we received yesterday and
OL,8,Fthere is now a general acceptance on
OL,9,Fbehalf of Mr Rainey that he killed Ms
OL,10,FMitchell. I use that term as opposed
OL,11,Fto murdering Ms Mitchell.
OL,13,F"It really is a medical defence now
OL,14,Fbased on diminished responsibility
OL,15,Fwhich centres round his state of mind
OL,16,Fat the time.
OL,18,F"Given the change in instructions we
OL,19,Fwill need to obtain an updated
OL,20,Fpsychiatric report from Dr Issac who
OL,21,Fhas previously examined Mr Rainey.''
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772474763
OL,3,CMan to admit killing Chloe Mitchell,
OL,4,Ccourt told
OL,6,FMr Connor said he had already spoken
OL,7,Fwith Dr Issac who said the earliest he
OL,8,Fcould consult with the defendant was
OL,9,FMarch 9, 2026, and he could have his
OL,10,Faddendum report completed by March 13,
OL,11,F2026.
OL,13,F"We will have to consider his report,
OL,14,Fthen consult with Mr Rainey and make a
OL,15,Fdecision on whether the addendum
OL,16,Freport will be served (on the Crown)
OL,17,Fand relied upon by us,'' explained Mr
OL,18,FConnor.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772474763
OL,3,CMan to admit killing Chloe Mitchell,
OL,4,Ccourt told
OL,6,F"The hope is that the report will be
OL,7,Frelied upon. Depending on the contents
OL,8,Fof that report, the prosecution may
OL,9,Fwant the defendant examined by their
OL,10,Fpsychiatrist Dr Brennan.''
OL,12,FMr Connor requested that the trial
OL,13,Fdate of March 9, 2026, be vacated in
OL,14,Flight of the new instructions from
OL,15,FRainey.
OL,17,FThe senior defence counsel asked that
OL,18,FRainey is not produced on the proposed
OL,19,Ftrial date as he is due his
OL,20,Fconsultation that day with Dr Issac.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772474763
OL,3,CMan to admit killing Chloe Mitchell,
OL,4,Ccourt told
OL,6,F"We could have him produced later in
OL,7,Fthe week so that he can re-arraigned
OL,8,Fon both counts he faces on the
OL,9,Findictment,'' said Mr Connor.
OL,11,F"He could be re-arraigned and maintain
OL,12,Fhis not guilty plea to murder but
OL,13,Fguilty to manslaughter by reason of
OL,14,Fdiminished responsibility,'' added Mr
OL,15,FConnor.
OL,17,FSenior prosecution counsel David
OL,18,FRussell KC said he was adopting a
OL,19,F"cautious approach'' to the change in
OL,20,Finstructions by the defendant.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772474763
OL,3,CMan to admit killing Chloe Mitchell,
OL,4,Ccourt told
OL,6,FHe told the court: "We rather have
OL,7,Fbeen here before because Dr Issac's
OL,8,Freport was relied on in this case from
OL,9,FApril 2025 and was obtained in the
OL,10,Fface of a trial which led to the trial
OL,11,Fnot proceeding.
OL,13,F"One of the issues in this case is the
OL,14,Fdefendant's inability to say what
OL,15,Fhappened (to Ms Mitchell).''
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772474763
OL,3,CMan to admit killing Chloe Mitchell,
OL,4,Ccourt told
OL,6,FMr Russell said the Crown's position
OL,7,Fwas that the court sits on March 10,
OL,8,F2026, in case the "accused changes his
OL,9,Fmind and decides not to see Dr Issac
OL,10,Fand we would need to be in a position
OL,11,Fto proceed with the trial''.
OL,13,FHe told the court that the Crown's
OL,14,Fposition would not change until there
OL,15,Fwere updated medical reports from both
OL,16,FDr Issac and Dr Brennan.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772474763
OL,3,CMan to admit killing Chloe Mitchell,
OL,4,Ccourt told
OL,6,FMr Russell pointed out that Dr Brennan
OL,7,Fis on leave until March 21, 2026 and
OL,8,Fhis first available appointment to see
OL,9,Fthe defendant would be from the week
OL,10,Fbeginning March 23, 2026.
OL,12,F"If all those commitments fall in
OL,13,Fplace, ie, the accused is seen by Dr
OL,14,FIssac, the re-arraignment, the two
OL,15,Fadditional reports, that looks like a
OL,16,Fbackstop of a trial starting in the
OL,17,Fnew term on April 13, 2026, which
OL,18,Fgives ample time for decisions to be
OL,19,Fmade,'' said Mr Russell.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
