PN,44911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772474763
OL,3,CMan to admit killing Chloe Mitchell,
OL,4,Ccourt told
OL,6,F"One way or another by that stage of
OL,7,FApril 13 we will know whether a trial
OL,8,Fis ready to proceed.''
OL,10,FIn response to prosecution
OL,11,Fsubmissions, Mr Connor said he
OL,12,Funderstood the Crown's position in
OL,13,Fwishing to maintain a trial date in
OL,14,Fcase Rainey changed his mind over
OL,15,Fentering a guilty plea to manslaughter
OL,16,Fby reason of diminished responsibility.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772474763
OL,3,CMan to admit killing Chloe Mitchell,
OL,4,Ccourt told
OL,6,F"The problem that I see with that is
OL,7,Fwe have received specific instructions
OL,8,Fand if my learned friend fears a
OL,9,Fchange of heart (by the defendant),
OL,10,Fthat would have implications for our
OL,11,Fcontinued representation,'' added Mr
OL,12,FConnor.
OL,14,FFollowing legal submissions, Madam
OL,15,FJustice McBride said the proposed
OL,16,Ftrial would not commence on March 9,
OL,17,F2026.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
