PN,44913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772474763
OL,3,CMan to admit killing Chloe Mitchell,
OL,4,Ccourt told
OL,6,FInstead, Rainey would be re-arraigned
OL,7,Fon March 12, 2026, and she ordered his
OL,8,Fproduction from custody to appear at
OL,9,FBelfast Crown Court.
OL,11,FThanking counsel for alerting her to
OL,12,Fprogress in the case, Madam Justice
OL,13,FMcBride said: "I think it is a welcome
OL,14,Fdevelopment and one I hope is welcomed
OL,15,Fby the family.''
OL,17,FChloe Mitchell's remains were found
OL,18,Fdays after she went missing.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
