CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1772474763
OL,3,CMan to admit killing Chloe Mitchell,
OL,4,Ccourt told
OL,6,FShe was last seen alive on CCTV in
OL,7,FBallymena town centre in the early
OL,8,Fhours of June 3, 2023 and an extensive
OL,9,Fsearch operation was launched by the
OL,10,FPSNI.
OL,12,FDetectives investigating her
OL,13,Fdisappearance later launched a murder
OL,14,Finquiry after human remains were
OL,15,Fdiscovered in Ballymena.
OL,17,FThis led officers to attend a flat in
OL,18,Fthe James Street area of the town
OL,19,Fwhich prompted Rainey's arrest.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/15
